@prefix core: <https://cns.dev/core#> .
@prefix res: <https://cns.dev/resilience#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

res:Retry a rdfs:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf core:Primitive .
res:CircuitBreaker a rdfs:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf core:Primitive .
res:RateLimiter a rdfs:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf core:Primitive .
